You are writing a modernized, AI-driven, user-friendly personal finance management system.

This project is a Next.js-based web application for personal finance tracking and analysis.

Using Stack:

## Frontend Framework
- Next.js 15.3.3 (App Router)
- React 19
- TypeScript 5
- TailwindCSS 4

## UI Components & Styling
- Lucide React (Icon library)
- Geist & Geist Mono fonts
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Modern card-based layout with shadows and rounded corners

Before starting, you need to know the current technical stack structure. Read tailwindcss to understand the design style.